### Popup UI

#### [MODIFY] [App.tsx](file:///Users/md.khaledbin/Practices/Chrome%20Extensions/Focus/src/App.tsx)

- Remove the locale-based "Dictionaries" list showing multiple locales
- Show a single status: "English Dictionary" with loading progress indicator during first-time import
